tel" title="bessahotel"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/sponsors/xGF-Hotels.jpg.pagespeed.ic.e7CphrHqC0.jpg" alt="GF-Hotels" title="GF-Hotels"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/sponsors/xGHL-Hoteles.jpg.pagespeed.ic.8uyti2RoBa.jpg" alt="GHL-Hoteles" title="GHL-Hoteles"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/sponsors/xGleneagle-Group.jpg.pagespeed.ic.hKwdbkrcvU.jpg" alt="Gleneagle-Group" title="Gleneagle-Group"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xH-Hotels.png.pagespeed.ic.thC9crmu6v.png" alt="H-Hotels" title="H-Hotels"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xHighgate,P20logo.png.pagespeed.ic.NhoTXmFYsY.png" alt="Highgate" title="Highgate"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xjaz-hotels.png.pagespeed.ic.FxB6YAad2t.png" alt="Jaz Hotel Group" title="Jaz Hotel Group"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xJupiter.png.pagespeed.ic.bsv_ecEPY_.png" alt="jupiter" title="jupiter"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/sponsors/xMama-shelter.jpg.pagespeed.ic.1jHm7c6OFE.jpg" alt="Mama Shelter" title="Mama Shelter"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xpalladium-s.png.pagespeed.ic.2Lon4QmaJr.png" alt="palladium" title="palladium"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/sponsors/xPartouche-hotels.jpg.pagespeed.ic.i0cMRp5oZD.jpg" alt="partouche" title="partouche"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xPickalbatros,P20Logo.png.pagespeed.ic.Jx66k9YSt7.png" alt="Pickalbatros" title="Pickalbatros"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xprecise-hotels.png.pagespeed.ic.7JkwaioMdF.png" alt="precise hotels" title="precise hotels"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/sponsors/xHotelposeidon.jpg.pagespeed.ic.n2cGaElm1O.jpg" alt="poseidon" title="poseidon"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xpullman-part.png.pagespeed.ic.a731YBmdrT.png" alt="pullman" title="pullman"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/sponsors/xsofital-slide.png.pagespeed.ic.2Dan92QIUU.png" alt="sofital" title="sofital"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/sponsors/xValentin-HR.jpg.pagespeed.ic.8jxBnLgiiK.jpg" alt="Valentin-HR" title="Valentin-HR"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xwarwick-partners.png.pagespeed.ic.-42YuydAKn.png" alt="warwick" title="warwick"/></div><div class="partner-item"><img src="/storage/app/media/xhyatt-inclusive.png.pagespeed.ic.B4naAajtH6.png" alt="hyatt inclusive" title="hyatt inclusive"/></div></ul></div></div><style>.partners-section{overflow:hidden;padding:20px 0;background:#fff;margin-top:0}.partners-track-container{width:100%;overflow:hidden}.partners-track{display:flex;animation:scroll 100s linear infinite;width:max-content}.partner-item{flex-shrink:0;margin:0 20px}.partner-item img{width:100%;height:auto;object-fit:contain}@keyframes scroll{0%{transform:translateX(0)}100%{transform:translateX(-50%)}}.partners-track:hover{animation-play-state:paused}.partners-track{will-change:transform;transform:translate3d(0,0,0)}</style></div><hr class="quinta-home__separator"><!-- Q-Services Section --><section class="quinta-home__section quinta-home__section--services"><div><div class="container"><div class="quinta-home__services-head"><h2 class="quinta-home__section-title" style="margin:0">Collect, update, process, and share hotel data</h2><div class="quinta-home__section-subtitle"><p><strong>Quinta&nbsp;</strong>(formerly Quicktext) is the only platform designed to <strong>collect, update, process, and distribute hotel data for the AI world</strong>,</p><p>ensuring hotels are visible, trusted, and chosen by AI where decisions and bookings happen.</p></div></div><div class="quinta-home__carousel"><input type="radio" name="carousel" id="slide1" checked><input type="radio" name="carousel" id="slide2"><input type="radio" name="carousel" id="slide3"><input type="radio" name="carousel" id="slide4"><input type="radio" name="carousel" id="slide5"><div class="quinta-home__cards"><article class="quinta-home__card"><h3 class="quinta-home__card-title">Q-Data</h3><p class="quinta-home__card-desc"><p>Q-Data is the only <strong>hotel data platform</strong> designed for modern search and all AI ecosystems. Q-Data structures, qualifies, and continuously updates 3700+ data points per hotel into a single, trusted source of truth, ensuring AI engines and agents can accurately understand, and compare hotels with confidence.</p></p><a href="/q-data/" class="quinta-home__card-link">Learn more →</a></article><article class="quinta-home__card"><h3 class="quinta-home__card-title">Q-Channel</h3><p class="quinta-home__card-desc"><p>Q-Channel is the <strong>hotel data distribution solution</strong> built for the AI era. It synchronizes and distributes Q-Data across all digital channels, third-party platforms, and public and private AI environments, ensuring hotel data remains consistent, structured, and always up to date wherever AI searches, compares, and books.</p></p><a href="/q-channel/" class="quinta-home__card-link">Learn more →</a></article><article class="quinta-home__card"><h3 class="quinta-home__card-title">Q-SEO</h3><p class="quinta-home__card-desc"><p>Q-SEO automatically generates and continuously updates multilingual, structured FAQs directly on the hotel website, based on real guest questions. By aligning on-site content with how users and AI engines search, it boosts SEO, AEO, and AI visibility, driving<strong>&nbsp;more qualified traffic and direct bookings</strong>.</p></p><a href="/q-seo/" class="quinta-home__card-link">Learn more →</a></article><article class="quinta-home__card"><h3 class="quinta-home__card-title">Q-Sales</h3><p class="quinta-home__card-desc"><p>Q-Sales <strong>centralizes all leads generated by Velma</strong> into a single hub and tracks their conversion into bookings. It follows each lead from first contact to confirmation, whether the booking is completed by the sales team, the call center, or directly by Velma, providing full visibility on performance and ROI.</p></p><a href="/q-sales/" class="quinta-home__card-link">Learn more →</a></article><article class="quinta-home__card"><h3 class="quinta-home__card-title">Q-Task</h3><p class="quinta-home__card-desc"><p>Q-Task <strong>coordinates guest requests</strong> handled by Velma. It assigns, prioritizes, and tracks operational tasks, streamlines internal communication, and connects with leading hotel task management systems.</p></p><a href="/q-task/" class="quinta-home__card-link">Learn more →</a></article></div><div class="quinta-home__carousel-dots"><label for="slide1"></label><label for="slide2"></label><label for="slide3"></label><label for="slide4"></label><label for="slide5"></label></div></div><div class="quinta-home__section-footer"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/products-solutions" class="quinta-home__head-cta">All solutions</a></div></div><script>(function(){var c=5,e=1,n=9000;function r(){e++;if(e>c){e=1};var t=document.getElementById('slide'+e);if(t){t.checked=!0}};var t=setInterval(r,n),a=document.querySelectorAll('.quinta-home__carousel-dots label');a.forEach(function(a){a.addEventListener('click',function(){clearInterval(t);var a=this.getAttribute('for');e=parseInt(a.replace('slide',''));t=setInterval(r,n)})})})();</script></div></section><hr class="quinta-home__separator"><!-- Key Metrics Section --><div><section class="quinta-home__section quinta-home__section--metrics"><div class="container"><div class="quinta-home__metrics-head"><h2>The numbers speak for themselves</h2></div><div class="quinta-home__metrics-grid"><div class="quinta-home__metric-card"><div class="quinta-home__metric-value">$1.05B</div><div class="quinta-home__metric-label"><p>Booking leads <br>generated</p></div><div class="quinta-home__metric-footnote">in the last 12 months</div></div><div class="quinta-home__metric-card"><div class="quinta-home__metric-value">ROI x17</div><div class="quinta-home__metric-label"><p>Return on <br>Investment</p></div><div class="quinta-home__metric-footnote">$100 invested = $1,700</div></div><div class="quinta-home__metric-card"><div class="quinta-home__metric-value">3,700</div><div class="quinta-home__metric-label"><p>Data points <br>per hotel</p></div><div class="quinta-home__metric-footnote">Most comprehensive in the industry</div></div><div class="quinta-home__metric-card"><div class="quinta-home__metric-value">38</div><div class="quinta-home__metric-label"><p>Native <br>languages</p></div><div class="quinta-home__metric-footnote">AI support worldwide</div></div></div></div></section></div><hr class="quinta-home__separator"><section class="quinta-home__section quinta-home__section--casestudies postpage"><div class="container"><div class="quinta-home__casestudies-head quinta-home__flex-header"><h2 style="margin:0">Data in action: Client success stories</h2></div><section class="post-velma"><div class="row post"><div class="col-lg-12"><div class="flex-box"><div class="post-content "><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/sofitel-fiji-quinta-ai-integration/"><img class="image-post" src="https://www.quinta.im/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/denarau-Island-Fiji-sofitel-cs.png.pagespeed.ce.1u-B8qOKGw.png" alt="blog image" loading="lazy"/></a></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/sofitel-fiji-quinta-ai-integration/"><strong> Less tasks, more time: Sofitel Fiji relies on Quinta AI</strong></a></h3><p>Located on the stunning Denarau Island in Fiji, Sofitel Fiji Resort &amp; Spa is synonymous with luxurious tropical escapes and exceptional service. In late 2023, the resort partnered with Quinta to integrate its AI-powered virtual assistant, transforming guest communication and streamlining operati[...]</p><a class="post-button" href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/sofitel-fiji-quinta-ai-integration/"> Read more</a></div></div></div><div class="post-content "><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/warwick-picks-quinta-to-scale-multi-property-ai-solution/"><img class="image-post" src="https://www.quinta.im/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/warwick-cs-new.png.pagespeed.ce.L-a5CBuA6W.png" alt="blog image" loading="lazy"/></a></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/warwick-picks-quinta-to-scale-multi-property-ai-solution/"><strong> Warwick picks Quinta to scale multi-property AI solution </strong></a></h3><p>Warwick Hotels and Resorts has a proven track record of over 40 years for delivering experienced personalized hospitality and outperforming results in hotel management, starting from its first hotel, the Warwick New York, acquired in 1980. Following the New York flagship, the Warwick Paris near the [...]</p><a class="post-button" href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/warwick-picks-quinta-to-scale-multi-property-ai-solution/"> Read more</a></div></div></div><div class="post-content "><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/palladium-hotel-group-transforms-lead-generation-with-quinta/"><img class="image-post" src="https://www.quinta.im/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/palladium-cs-2.png.pagespeed.ce.g0vwQM18Ye.png" alt="blog image" loading="lazy"/></a></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/palladium-hotel-group-transforms-lead-generation-with-quinta/"><strong> Palladium Hotel Group adopts “game changer” AI to increase revenue</strong></a></h3><p>Palladium Hotel Group Director Corporate Digital &amp; MadTech Antonio Andujar Gomez wanted to unlock new revenue opportunities by identifying and addressing guests&#8217; needs at every stage in their travel cycle. Palladium Hotel Group is a Spanish hotel company that operates a collection of hotel[...]</p><a class="post-button" href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/palladium-hotel-group-transforms-lead-generation-with-quinta/"> Read more</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="quinta-home__section-footer"><a href="/blog/category/case-studies/" class="button-link btn outline-d">More data experience</a></div></div></section><hr class="quinta-home__separator quinta-home__separator--before-velma"><!-- Velma Section --><div><section class="quinta-home__section quinta-home__section--velma"><div class="container"><div class="quinta-home__velma"><div class="quinta-home__velma-content"><div class="quinta-home__velma-desc"><h2>Meet Velma, <br>Your AI Hotel <br>Booking Assistant</h2><p>Hospitality’s most advanced AI, built on 3,700 data points and hybrid intelligence. Velma doesn’t talk. She collects information and converts.</p></div></div></div><div class="quinta-home__section-footer"><a class="quinta-home__velma-cta button-link btn outline-d" href="https://www.quinta.im/about-us/">About Us</a></div></div></section></div><hr class="quinta-home__separator"><section class="quinta-home__section quinta-home__section--events postpage"><div class="container"><section class="post-velma"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-12"><div class="quinta-home__flex-header"><h2 style="margin:0">All Quinta's events </h2></div></div></div><div class="row post post-home"><div class="col-lg-12"><div class="flex-box"><div class="post-content"><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><img class="image-post" src="/storage/app/media//xdata-is-the-new-black-paris-edition,P20-web.jpg.pagespeed.ic.aKrrXQWMD6.png" alt=" Data is the New Black - Paris Edition" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title">PARIS, FRANCE - JUNE 9, 2026</h3><p class="decription-post"><p>Data is the New Black (Paris) - No hype.</p><p>Just what really changes for hotels. <br>■ How guests choose hotels today, <br>■ What data actually impacts visibility and bookings, <br>■ Why consistency matters more than content volume, <br>■ What hotels should realistically do now with data, PMS, AI and BI,</p><p>For hoteliers, consultants, and revenue <br>&amp; marketing teams seeking clarity over complexity.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Date</strong>:&nbsp;Tuesday, June 9, 2026</p><p><strong>Time</strong>: from 15:00 to 19:00 CET</p><p><strong>Location</strong>: Business France, 77 bd St Jacques Paris, France.</p><p><br></p></p><div><a class="post-button" href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/billets-data-is-the-new-black-1982899910009?aff=oddtdtcreator" target="_blank">Register here</a></div></div></div></div><div class="post-content"><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><img class="image-post" src="/storage/app/media//xtechnology-,P20Innovation,P20and,P20entrepreneurship-Day-The,P20Bay-web.png.pagespeed.ic.KbxeKfSLQa.jpg" alt=" MEET QUINTA AT TIED@THE BAY" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title">MIAMI, FLORIDA - APRIL 16, 2026</h3><p class="decription-post"><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">We’re excited to announce that <strong>Quinta </strong>will be sponsoring TIED@THE BAY: Technology, Innovation &amp; Entrepreneurship Day.</p><p dir="ltr">Hosted by<a href="https://hospitality.fiu.edu/">&nbsp;FIU Chaplin School of Hospitality &amp; Tourism Management</a>, <a href="https://hftpsfl.org/">HFTP South Florida</a>,<a href="https://www.hsmaisouthflorida.org/">&nbsp;HSMAI South Florida</a> &amp; <a href="https://frla.org" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Florida Restaurant and Lodging Association (FRLA)</a> bringing together industry leaders, entrepreneurs, and innovators to explore the future of technology in hospitality and beyond.</p><p dir="ltr">Join us at the panel discussion or the exhibit table to discover how <strong>data management and AI&nbsp;</strong>are empowering hotels to enhance guest experiences, optimize operations, and help generate more direct revenue in the Agentic Era.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Date</strong>: April 16, 2026</p><p><strong>Location</strong>: Kovens Conference Center FIU Biscayne Bay Campus, North Miami, Florida</p><p><br></p></p><div><a class="post-button" href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/technology-innovation-and-entrepreneurship-day-the-bay-tickets-1982883323398?aff=oddtdtcreator" target="_blank">Register here</a></div></div></div></div><div class="post-content"><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><img class="image-post" src="/storage/app/media//xHotel,P20Digital,P20Summit,P202028-web.png.pagespeed.ic.GBvN0pFc2I.jpg" alt=" Meet Quinta at Hotel Digital Summit 2026" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title">Bali, Indonesia - APRIL 9, 2026</h3><p class="decription-post"><p>AI agents will soon search, compare and book on behalf of travelers.</p><p>If your hotel data is not structured and synchronized, you will become invisible.</p><p>The solution is not more AI it is a canonical data infrastructure.</p><p>In the agentic era, only hotels with structured, queryable and real-time distributed data will appear in final selections.</p><p>AI is not the advantage. Data quality and distribution are.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Date</strong>: April 9, 2026</p><p><strong>Location</strong>: The Magani Hotel and Spa Bali, Indonesia.</p><p><br></p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="quinta-home__section-footer"><a href="/we-are-running/" class="button-link btn outline-d">We are running</a></div></div></section><hr class="quinta-home__separator"><section class="section3"><div><div class="container"><section class="post-velma"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-12"><h2>Why Quinta?</h2></div></div><div class="row post"><div class="col-lg-12"><div class="flex-box"><div class="post-content"><div class="post"><div class="qt-block"><h3 class="post-title">The one and only structured, distributed hotel data solution</h3><p><p dir="ltr">Quinta transforms hotel data into a structured, distributed, and AI-ready asset, ensuring visibility, consistency, and performance where booking decisions are now made.</p><ul><li><span dir="ltr">Structure and share hotels’ data,</span>&nbsp;</li><li>Interact automatically with customers,</li><li>Optimise sales, content, and marketing,</li><li>Supply data for<strong>&nbsp;LLM, AI agent&nbsp;</strong>and<strong>&nbsp;business intelligence</strong>.</li></ul></p></div></div></div><div class="post-content"><div class="post"><div class="qt-block"><h3 class="post-title">Validated and awarded in the industry globally</h3><p><p>Since 2017, Quinta's technologically advanced solutions have been recognised around the world, in particular at the Global Tech Awards in Austin, Texas, the <a aria-label="Lien Premium Travel Awards" href="https://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4108013.html" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank" title="https://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4108013.html">Premium Travel Awards</a> in Shenzen, China, and at the International Tourism Meeting in Paris, France. Last April, <a aria-label="Lien Quinta was ranked No. 2" href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/quinta-ranks-second-among-ai-startups-in-france/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="https://www.quinta.im/blog/quinta-ranks-second-among-ai-startups-in-france/">Quinta was ranked No. 2</a> nationally (among 13,000 companies) in France for its leadership in AI.</p></p></div></div></div><div class="post-content"><div class="post"><div class="qt-block"><h3 class="post-title">Since 2017, Quinta is used by the world&#039;s largest hotel groups</h3><p><p>Accor (FRA), H-Hotels (GER), Hyatt (USA), Highgate (USA), Jaz Hotels (EGY) Palladium (SPA), Precise (DEU), Santa Fe (MEX), Warwick (USA).<span dir="ltr"><br>With a recommendation rate of 96% according to the Hotel Tech Report, <strong>Quinta </strong>is regularly ranked #1 in the field of </span><a href="https://www.quinta.im/ai-for-hotels/"><span dir="ltr"><strong>AI in the hospitality industry</strong></span></a><span dir="ltr"><strong>.</strong></span></p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></section><hr class="quinta-home__separator"><section class="quinta-home__section quinta-home__section--blog postpage"><div class="container"><div class="quinta-home__flex-header"><h2 style="margin:0">Insights on AI, generative search, agents, and SEO</h2></div><section class="post-velma"><div class="row post"><div class="col-lg-12"><div class="flex-box"><div class="post-content "><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/ai-agents-hospitality-hotel-data/"><img class="image-post" src="https://www.quinta.im/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/xai-agents-are-coming-to-hospitality.png.pagespeed.ic.NFE_TB7EZk.png" alt="blog image" loading="lazy"/></a></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/ai-agents-hospitality-hotel-data/"><strong> AI agents are coming to hospitality. Are you ready? </strong></a></h3><p>AI agents will soon search, compare, and book on behalf of travelers. If your data is not structured, synchronized, and readable by these agents, you will become invisible. The solution is not more AI. The solution is better data infrastructure. Hospitality is entering the agentic era… AI agents ar[...]</p><a class="post-button" href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/ai-agents-hospitality-hotel-data/" aria-label="AI agents are coming to hospitality. Are you ready? "> Learn more</a></div></div></div><div class="post-content "><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/data-is-king-data-distribution-is-king-kong/"><img class="image-post" src="https://www.quinta.im/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/blog-data-is-king.png.pagespeed.ce.BRrlCfgFOD.png" alt="blog image" loading="lazy"/></a></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/data-is-king-data-distribution-is-king-kong/"><strong> Data is King, Data Distribution is King Kong</strong></a></h3><p>Throughout 2025, we have all been inundated by continual announcements about AI: advances from OpenAI, initiatives from Google, the rise of Perplexity, developments by Booking and Expedia… and we have been overwhelmed by recommendations on how to follow each of these evolutions. It is now time to st[...]</p><a class="post-button" href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/data-is-king-data-distribution-is-king-kong/" aria-label="Data is King, Data Distribution is King Kong"> Learn more</a></div></div></div><div class="post-content "><div class="post"><div class="img-fluid"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/mcp-for-hotels-model-context-protocol/"><img class="image-post" src="https://www.quinta.im/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/blog-MCP-WTF.png.pagespeed.ce.i5b1Bcuved.png" alt="blog image" loading="lazy"/></a></div><div class="content"><h3 class="post-title"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/mcp-for-hotels-model-context-protocol/"><strong> But what exactly is a MCP?</strong></a></h3><p>Today, you have to juggle several tools: Part 1: Which major problem will the MCPs solve? MCP = Toolbox It is a case of all these tools (PMS, CRS, CRM, Q-Data) gathered into a single, smart, well-organized, and easily accessible box. Result Conversational agents or platforms (Gemini, ChatGPT, Perple[...]</p><a class="post-button" href="https://www.quinta.im/blog/mcp-for-hotels-model-context-protocol/" aria-label="But what exactly is a MCP?"> Learn more</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="quinta-home__section-footer"><a href="/blog/" class="button-link btn outline-d">More articles</a></div></div></section><!-- CTA Section --><section class="quinta-home__section quinta-home__section--cta"><div class="quinta-home__cta-overlay"></div><div class="container"><div class="quinta-home__cta-box"><h2 class="quinta-home__cta-title">Where hotel data<br> becomes bookings</h2><div class="quinta-home__cta-buttons"><a href="https://www.quinta.im/contact" class="quinta-home__cta-btn quinta-home__cta-btn--primary"> Contact us</a></div></div></div></section><hr class="quinta-home__separator quinta-home__separator--faq-mobile"><section class="quinta-home__section quinta-home__section--faq"><div><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8"><h2>FAQ</h2></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-12"><details><summary><h3><span class="faq-number">1.</span> What is Quinta?</h3></summary></h3><div class=""><div class="reponse"><p><p>Quinta (formerly Quicktext) is a hotel data management and distribution platform <br class="desktop-only-br">designed for the era of AI, Agentic AI, and the Model Context Protocol (MCP). <br class="desktop-only-br">It collects, structures, updates, and distributes more than 3,700 data points per hotel, <br class="desktop-only-br">creating a dataset that can be fully leveraged by AI engines and autonomous agents. <br class="desktop-only-br">This data is synchronized across the hotel’s website, OTAs, GDS, metasearch engines, <br class="desktop-only-br">and AI environments (ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity…). <br class="desktop-only-br">Thanks to this depth of structured data, Quinta serves as the optimal infrastructure for Agentic AI, <br class="desktop-only-br">generating greater visibility, qualified traffic, and direct bookings through Velma.</p></p></div></div></details><details><summary><h3><span class="faq-number">2.</span> Why is Quinta essential for AI search (AEO)?</h3></summary></h3><div class=""><div class="reponse"><p><p dir="ltr">AI Search (AEO – Answer Engine Optimization) relies on structured, reliable, and continuously updated data. </p><p dir="ltr">Without clean and properly distributed data, a hotel becomes invisible in AI-generated responses.</p><p dir="ltr">Quinta ensures a structure compliant with semantic web standards (Schema.org) and compatible with LLMs via MCP.</p><p dir="ltr">As a result, the hotel is recommended, compared, and selected within AI search environments and agentic AI systems.</p></p></div></div></details><details><summary><h3><span class="faq-number">3.</span> How does Quinta improve visibility in Google and AI platforms?</h3></summary></h3><div class=""><div class="reponse"><p><p dir="ltr">Quinta transforms hotel information into structured data that can be understood by Google and AI engines.</p><p dir="ltr">The platform synchronizes this data across all digital channels to ensure consistency and freshness.</p><p dir="ltr">This consistency strengthens SEO rankings and presence in generative responses (AEO).</p><p dir="ltr">The result: increased organic visibility and more qualified traffic.</p></p></div></div></details><details><summary><h3><span class="faq-number">4.</span> What business results does Quinta deliver to hotels?</h3></summary></h3><div class=""><div class="reponse"><p><p>A measurable increase in visibility on Google, AI Search, and agentic AI environments. <br class="desktop-only-br">More qualified traffic thanks to reliable, continuously updated data. <br class="desktop-only-br">Optimized conversion through Velma, the AI agent that turns visitors into qualified leads and bookings. <br class="desktop-only-br">Sustainable growth in direct revenue and reduced dependency on OTAs.</p></p></div></div></details></div></div></div></div></section></main><style>:root{--quinta-black:#0a0a0a;--quinta-white:#fff;--quinta-gray-100:#f9fafb;--quinta-gray-200:#d5dae1;--quinta-gray-400:#6a7282;--quinta-gold:#d4b116;--quinta-warning:#f8bb54}.quinta-home__separator{border:none;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right, #fff0 0%, #939393 50%, #fff0 100%);display:block;width:52%}.quinta-home{font-family:'Lato',sans-serif}.quinta-home__section--services{background:rgba(255,255,255,.57);padding:30px 0 40px}.quinta-home__section--casestudies{padding:30px 0 0}{padding:50px 0 0}.quinta-home__section--blog{padding:40px 0}.quinta-home__section-footer{text-align:center;padding-top:25px}.quinta-home__section--testimonials{padding:70px 0}.quinta-home__kicker{font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#4a5565;margin-bottom:10px}.quinta-home__kicker--light{color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}.quinta-home__section-title{font-family:'Caladea',serif;font-size:47px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 20px 0;line-height:1.2}.quinta-home__section-subtitle{font-size:18px}.quinta-home__services-head{margin-bottom:50px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;row-gap:10px}.quinta-home__services-head .quinta-home__kicker,.quinta-home__services-head .quinta-home__section-title,.quinta-home__services-head .quinta-home__section-subtitle{margin-bottom:0}.quinta-home__head-cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:15.6px 32px;border-radius:999px;background:#000;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-size:15.6px;font-weight:400;line-height:23.4px;white-space:nowrap;border:none}.quinta-home__head-cta:hover{color:#fff;opacity:.9;text-decoration:none}.quinta-home__cards{display:block}.quinta-home__carousel{position:relative;overflow:hidden;width:100%}.quinta-home__carousel input[type="radio"]{display:none}.quinta-home__cards{display:flex;transition:transform .5s ease-in-out;gap:60px}@keyframes autoSlide{0%,20%{transform:translateX(0);}25%,45%{transform:translateX(-347px);}50%,70%{transform:translateX(-694px);}75%,95%{transform:translateX(-1041px);}100%{transform:translateX(0);}}.quinta-home__cards{animation:autoSlide 24s infinite}.quinta-home__carousel:hover .quinta-home__cards{animation-play-state:paused}#slide1:checked ~ .quinta-home__cards{transform:translateX(0);animation:none}#slide2:checked ~ .quinta-home__cards{transform:translateX(-390px);animation:none}#slide3:checked ~ .quinta-home__cards{transform:translateX(-780px);animation:none}.quinta-home__carousel-dots{text-align:center;margin-top:30px}.quinta-home__carousel-dots label{display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;margin:0 5px;background:#d5dae1;border-radius:50