//]]></script><script src="https://www.quinta.im/themes/quicktext/assets/dist/js/vendor.js.pagespeed.jm.mVhA_z6-LH.js"></script><script src="https://www.quinta.im/themes/quicktext/assets/dist/js/app.js.pagespeed.jm.g0dUx_BXtL.js"></script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Organization","name":"Quinta","alternateName":"Quicktext","url":"https://www.quinta.im/","email":"hello@quinta.im","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.quinta.im/storage/app/media/signature/quinta-black.png"},"sameAs":["https://www.linkedin.com/company/quinta","https://www.instagram.com/quinta","https://x.com/quinta","https://www.youtube.com/@quinta"]}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebSite","url":"https://www.quinta.im/","name":"Quinta","inLanguage":"en"}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebPage","url":"https://www.quinta.im/","name":"The only platform designed to collect, update, process & share hotel data for the AI world.","inLanguage":"en"}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","inLanguage":"en","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is Quinta?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Quinta (formerly Quicktext) is a hotel data management and distribution platform designed for the era of AI, Agentic AI, and the Model Context Protocol (MCP). It collects, structures, updates, and distributes more than 3,700 data points per hotel, creating a dataset that can be fully leveraged by AI engines and autonomous agents. This data is synchronized across the hotel's website, OTAs, GDS, metasearch engines, and AI environments (ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity). Thanks to this depth of structured data, Quinta serves as the optimal infrastructure for Agentic AI, generating greater visibility, qualified traffic, and direct bookings through Velma."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why is Quinta essential for AI Search (AEO)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AI Search (AEO – Answer Engine Optimization) relies on structured, reliable, and continuously updated data. Without clean and properly distributed data, a hotel becomes invisible in AI-generated responses. Quinta ensures a structure compliant with semantic web standards (Schema.org) and compatible with LLMs via MCP. As a result, the hotel is recommended, compared, and selected within AI search environments and agentic AI systems."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does Quinta improve visibility in Google and AI platforms?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Quinta transforms hotel information into structured data that can be understood by Google and AI engines. The platform synchronizes this data across all digital channels to ensure consistency and freshness. This consistency strengthens SEO rankings and presence in generative responses (AEO). The result: increased organic visibility and more qualified traffic."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What concrete results does Quinta deliver to hotels?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Quinta delivers a measurable increase in visibility on Google, AI Search, and agentic AI environments. More qualified traffic comes from reliable, continuously updated data. Conversion is optimized through Velma, the AI agent that turns visitors into qualified leads and bookings. The outcome is sustainable growth in direct revenue and reduced dependency on OTAs."}}]}</script><script>document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',()=>{const buttons=document.querySelectorAll('.custom-dropdown-toggle-footer');const dropdowns=document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-content');const defaultDropdown=document.querySelector('#europe-numbers');defaultDropdown.classList.add('open');buttons.forEach(button=>{button.addEventListener('click',()=>{const targetId=button.getAttribute('data-target');const targetDropdown=document.querySelector(targetId);const isOpen=targetDropdown.classList.contains('open');dropdowns.forEach(dropdown=>{dropdown.classList.remove('open')});if(!isOpen){targetDropdown.classList.add('open')}})})})</script></body></html>